# Munglabs Blog + Comments Plan

## Architecture
- **Monolith repo** — No separate BE needed
- **Posts → Astro Content Collections (MDX)** — Files in `src/content/blog/`
- **Comments → Giscus** — GitHub Discussions-powered, zero backend

## Stack
- Astro Content Collections (schema validation, automatic routing)
- MDX for blog posts (supports JSX components inline)
- Giscus React component for comments
- Same design system (blue theme, Inter font, animations)

## Giscus Setup Required
1. Create or enable GitHub Discussions on a repo (e.g., `munglabs/munglabs-comments`)
2. Install Giscus app on that repo: https://giscus.app
3. Use generated config in `Giscus.tsx` component

