## File Structure
```
src/
├── content/
│   └── blog/
│       └── welcome-to-munglabs.mdx
├── content.config.ts
├── components/
│   ├── Giscus.tsx
│   └── ...existing
├── layouts/
│   ├── BlogPostLayout.astro
│   └── BaseLayout.astro
├── pages/
│   └── blog/
│       ├── index.astro
│       └── [...slug].astro
└── styles/
    └── global.css
```

## Blog Post Schema (Frontmatter)
- title: string
- description: string
- date: ISO date
- tags: string[]
- coverImage?: string

## Giscus Config (placeholder, update with real values from giscus.app)
- repo: "munglabs/munglabs-comments"
- repoId: (from giscus.app)
- category: "Announcements"
- categoryId: (from giscus.app)
- mapping: "pathname"
- reactions: enabled
- theme: "light" / "dark"
